    "apf.ew_sqrtNc_carrier_color_triplet",
    "apf.ew_scale_functional_independence",  # v24.3.314 - EW scale-FUNCTIONAL independence NO-GO [P_structural]: f=v_H/M_Pl as an expression in ledger structure is NOT fixed by the base {A1,MD,A2,BW,FD1-sc} + banked base-resting stack -- >=2 admissible structural completions (banked reading 246 GeV / full-power 8.9e-14 / rational 1.2e15 / transmutation-form 6.9e5), closed-world EXISTENCE direction (no .284 trap). Completes the no-go triptych: magnitude (rescaling) / prefactor (.177/.180) / FORM (this). K4 walker (the .305 shape) classifies the whole v_H-fixing surface (reservoir-family reading-conditional / measurement-completion / gate); .284 abelian regrade PINNED as falsifier hook. Identification (B) = proven-irreducible reading; smuggling guard prices future derivation claims. Banked as the audit-cleared salvage of the 2026-07-02 (A)/(B) walk (Move A uniformity REFUTED same session -- fermion counterexample, do-not-re-walk). 1 check.  # v24.3.185 - sqrt(N_c) carrier FORCED by the physical color-triplet trace [P_structural], CLOSES the last prefactor clause. a_Y/sqrt(b)=sqrt(N_c) (y_t cancels) is the physical trace ratio: a2=Sum N_c*Tr exact over H_F=C^96 (L_normalization_coefficient [P]), SU(3)/N_c=3/triplet quarks (Theorem_R/T_gauge/T_field [P]). sqrt(N_c) is basis-invariant; color-strip (countermodel B) is a different trace functional (color-average), not a basis change -> EXCLUDED. No-go v24.3.169 preserved INVERSION-ONLY (absolute y_t still not derivable). EW floor now FULLY forced (exponent .184 + measure .181 + Planck-norm .183 + carrier this); only the absolute Planck magnitude = one external input (route-b). 1 check.
